title: Departing Pentagon AI Chief Sounds Alarm on Overhyped AI Claims
description: In a parting address to the congressional hearing, Craig Martell, the Chief Digital and Artificial Intelligence Officer at the Pentagon, delivered a stark warning against the sensationalism surrounding artificial intelligence (AI).
